<li><small>Pearson, Karl (1911). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://archive.org/stream/academicaspectof00pear#page/n3/mode/2up"><i>The Academic Aspect of the Science of Eugenics: A Lecture Delivered to Undergraduates</i></a>. London: Dulau &amp; Co.</small></li>
