<li><small>Pearson, Karl (1912). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://archive.org/stream/darwinismmedical1912pear#page/n1/mode/2up"><i>Darwinism, Medical Progress and Eugenics. The Cavendish Lecture: An Address to the Medical Profession</i></a>. London: Dulau &amp; Co.</small></li>
