<li><small>Pearson, Karl (1914). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://archive.org/stream/firststudyofstat00pearrich#page/n3/mode/2up"><i>On the Handicapping of the First-born: Being a Lecture Delivered at the Galton Laboratory</i></a>. London: Dulau &amp; Co.</small></li>
